java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<DataRecord>, java.util.Collection<DataRecord>, java.util.List<DataRecord>, java.util.RandomAccess
public class DataSelection
extends java.util.ArrayList<DataRecord>

The class which stores a selection of DataRecords. This class is a list of DataRecord objects, and also provides methods supporting encoding and decoding of selections as BitSet objects.

Author:
Curran Kelleher
